snippet.title: Iris is on the kidnapper's trail! | Private Iris Case 5: Amber's Abduction (Part 3)
snippet.description:
Private Iris and Danton are getting closer to finding Amber's kidnapper as they discover his motivation for his crimes. But Iris's dad Warren doesn't think Iris and Danton should be on the case as it's getting too dangerous. He may be right.

Starring:
Teetin Villanueva as Private Iris (and all female voices)
https://instagram.com/teetinv
#teetinv #teetinvillanueva

Jamie Bautista as Danton Cord (and all male voices)
https://instagram.com/ntu150

Story by:
Jamie Bautista

Art by:
Arnold Arre
https://www.youtube.com/user/arnoldarrefilms
#arnoldarre

Editing and Sound Design by:
Jamie Bautista
